---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Digital Savings Revolution">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <img 
      src="/images/blog/digital-savings.jpg"
      alt="Digital Savings Revolution"
      class="w-full h-[400px] object-cover rounded-lg mb-8"
    />
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
      The Digital Savings Revolution: How Technology is Changing the Way We Save
    </h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">December 9, 2024</p>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <p>
        Gone are the days of clipping paper coupons from newspapers. The digital age has transformed how we save money, making it easier and more efficient than ever.
      </p>

      <h2>The Rise of Digital Coupons</h2>
      <p>
        Digital coupons have revolutionized the savings game:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Instant availability</li>
        <li>No printing required</li>
        <li>Easy organization</li>
        <li>Personalized offers</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Mobile Apps Leading the Way</h2>
      <p>
        Today's must-have savings apps:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Store loyalty apps</li>
        <li>Cashback platforms</li>
        <li>Price comparison tools</li>
        <li>Digital coupon aggregators</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 my-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Did You Know?</h3>
        <p>
          Over 80% of shoppers now use digital coupons and savings apps. Learn more in our <a href="/digital-couponing-guide" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80">Digital Couponing Guide</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2>Smart Shopping with Technology</h2>
      <p>
        Modern tools for maximum savings:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Browser extensions for automatic coupon testing</li>
        <li>Price tracking alerts</li>
        <li>Digital receipt scanning for rebates</li>
        <li>AI-powered deal recommendations</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>The Future of Savings</h2>
      <p>
        Emerging trends in digital savings:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Personalized AI shopping assistants</li>
        <li>Voice-activated deal searching</li>
        <li>Augmented reality price comparison</li>
        <li>Blockchain-based reward systems</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="bg-primary/5 rounded-lg p-6 my-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Start Saving Today</h3>
        <p>
          Ready to embrace digital savings? Check out our <a href="/store-rewards-guide" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80">Store Rewards Guide</a> for tips on combining digital and traditional savings methods!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
